fix(templates): React.children -> React.Children (#818)

@justingreenberg had a typo in ac1f6346535534e7061a8ba9b15a0f246a020a77
which broke the cleaned app. Closes #817

Renamed all files

This makes importing files from other files much easier and nicer, e.g.

import HomePage from 'HomePage/HomePage.react';

now is

import HomePage from 'HomePage';

Use index.js files to export components.

This allows importing a directory.

```diff
-import Img from 'Img/Img.react';
+import Img from 'Img';
```
